.section.section--mark#advant(style="background-image:url('img/item-1.jpg')")
	.main-cont
		.section-title.section-title--img(data-aos="fade-in" data-aos-delay="300" data-aos-duration="2000") 10 reasons to choose
			img(src="img/logo-cpi.svg", alt="")
		.why-text.text(data-aos="fade-in" data-aos-delay="600" data-aos-duration="2000")
			p CPI box Creatio combines in a single interface all the necessary tools for automating the mechanism for evaluating the current level of maturity of processes and their capabilities.
